<br>
I'd save your cash until you hit 51 and then buy, or just buy now and equip it when you hit 51.  The SVM is reasonably quick, on average the proc goes off at least once per fight (it is resistable however) and there is some nice stats on it.  A very good main-hander that should see you through until you get your epic.<br>
<br>
The GSC is still a very reasonable weapon at 49.  If you must buy something to use now, and you can handle the weight, grab an CGM, and sell it when you hit 51 and buy an SVM.  I liked mine a lot.  If you want to work on HtH, and can track down a Fist of Iron, it is a slightly better option, and should be priced slightly above a SVM. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udevaili.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Devaili</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/14/02 5:15:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11850.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spiked Velium Mallet?</span><hr size=1> Many thanks so far for advise, someone sold on my server for 10k 2 hours ago =) Think i got good buy.  1 lvl and 2 gold to go!  Got enough pp left over to maybe get a Adamantite club for offhand, or should i stick with the Sos? heres combos.. i could have if i did buy.<br>
